These are release notes for Altoros Log Search for Pivotal Cloud Foundry (PCF).

##<a id="ver"></a> v0.207.7

**Release Date:** June 28, 2017

Features included in this release:

* Internally, Altoros Log Search for PCF now refers to the Ops Manager Director by hostname instead of by IP address.
  This corrects an issue where the tile could not communicate with the Ops Manager Director if the IP address changed.

